data.description:
WOW!! Beautifully updated and maintained 4bed/2bath home with a separate 1bed/2 bath guest house and a pool, on just under an acre! Main house 2830 sq ft, guest house 998 sq ft, totaling 3,828 sq ft! Previously completely remodeled from the walls in, and the current owners have added on to the updates! The main house received a new roof, wood look tile flooring, and gorgeous Renewal by Anderson windows and doors, and in addition, the guest house was remodeled to make it a true 1 bedroom as well as new flat roof and updated flooring - all within the last three years! Brand-new carpet was also just installed in the bedrooms of the main house in February 2024!  The main house kitchen has granite countertops and an island that looks onto the dining and family area; great for entertaining. Split floorplan, Cathedral Ceilings, spacious master with walk in closet and large master bath with dual sinks and garden tub all add to the beauty of the home. There is also a large bright living room with patio doors to the spacious covered back patio where you can enjoy the mountain views and look over your glistening POOL! The heated 20x40 pool is completely fenced in and has an indoor pump house. The incredibly cute guest house is completely separate, with its own gate entry into the yard. In Law Suite? Airbnb property? Long term rental? The choice is yours! The property also has an 8x12 storage shed, an RV gate, and water and 30 Amp electric hookups! With so much to offer, come see this beautiful property before it is gone! 
(Living room wood burning fireplace in main house has not been operational since prior to current homeowner. Guest house washer and dryer do not convey).
